### Patient Management Service — Specialty Endpoints
### Requires: REST Client extension (humao.rest-client)
### Only "admin" role can create, update, or deactivate specialties.
### All authenticated users can read.

@baseUrl      = http://localhost:8001
@token        = PASTE_YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@adminToken   = PASTE_ADMIN_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@specialtyId  = PASTE_SPECIALTY_UUID_HERE
@specialtyCode = CARDIO


# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# POST /api/v1/specialties  — Create a new specialty (admin only)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 1. Create specialty — Cardiology
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/specialties
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "code": "CARDIO",
  "name": "Cardiology",
  "category": "terapeutica",
  "description": "Diagnosis and treatment of heart and cardiovascular system disorders."
}

###

### 2. Create specialty — Neurology
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/specialties
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "code": "NEURO",
  "name": "Neurology",
  "category": "terapeutica",
  "description": "Diagnosis and treatment of disorders of the nervous system."
}

###

### 3. Create specialty — General Surgery
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/specialties
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "code": "GEN_SURG",
  "name": "General Surgery",
  "category": "quirurgica",
  "description": "Surgical treatment of abdominal organs and related structures."
}

###

### 4. Create specialty — Family Medicine (Primary Care)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/specialties
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "code": "FAM_MED",
  "name": "Family Medicine",
  "category": "atencion_primaria"
}

###

### 5. Create specialty — expect 409 Conflict (duplicate code)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/specialties
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "code": "CARDIO",
  "name": "Cardiology Duplicate",
  "category": "terapeutica"
}

###

### 6. Create specialty — expect 422 Unprocessable Entity (invalid code format)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/specialties
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "code": "invalid code!",
  "name": "Bad Code",
  "category": "terapeutica"
}

###

### 7. Create specialty — expect 403 Forbidden (non-admin token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/specialties
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "code": "FORBIDDEN",
  "name": "Should Fail",
  "category": "otra"
}


# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# GET /api/v1/specialties  — List all specialties
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

###

### 8. List all specialties (active and inactive)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/specialties
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 9. List only active specialties
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/specialties?active_only=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 10. List specialties — expect 401 Unauthorized (missing token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/specialties


# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# GET /api/v1/specialties/{specialty_id}  — Get specialty by UUID
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

###

### 11. Get specialty by UUID — replace specialtyId at the top
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/specialties/{{specialtyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 12. Get specialty by UUID — expect 404 Not Found
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/specialties/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# GET /api/v1/specialties/code/{code}  — Get specialty by code
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

###

### 13. Get specialty by code
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/specialties/code/{{specialtyCode}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 14. Get specialty by code — expect 404 Not Found
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/specialties/code/DOES_NOT_EXIST
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# PATCH /api/v1/specialties/{specialty_id}  — Partial update (admin only)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

###

### 15. Update specialty name
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/specialties/{{specialtyId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Cardiology & Electrophysiology"
}

###

### 16. Update specialty description and category
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/specialties/{{specialtyId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "description": "Updated description including electrophysiology sub-specialty.",
  "category": "terapeutica"
}

###

### 17. Update specialty — expect 404 Not Found
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/specialties/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Ghost Specialty"
}

###

### 18. Update specialty — expect 403 Forbidden (non-admin token)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/specialties/{{specialtyId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Should Be Rejected"
}


# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# DELETE /api/v1/specialties/{specialty_id}  — Deactivate (soft-delete, admin only)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

###

### 19. Deactivate (soft-delete) a specialty — sets is_active=false
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/specialties/{{specialtyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 20. Deactivate specialty — expect 404 Not Found
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/specialties/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 21. Deactivate specialty — expect 403 Forbidden (non-admin token)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/specialties/{{specialtyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
